    <title>指针1</title>
    <url>/2025/03/18/%E6%8C%87%E9%92%881/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h1 id="指针1"><a href="#指针1" class="headerlink" title="指针1"></a>指针1</h1><ul>
<li>其实指针就是内存地址。</li>
<li>在代码中经常会用一个变量将这个内存地址存储起来，这个变量就是指针变量。</li>
<li>但是注意，指针是指针，是内存地址，指针变量是存储内存地址的变量。</li>
<li>因为指针变量是存储的地址，所以不能把数值赋值给指针变量，而是应该把数值所在的地址赋值给指针变量</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="指针变量"><a href="#指针变量" class="headerlink" title="指针变量"></a>指针变量</h2><p><em><em>数据类型</em> 变量名</em>*</p>
<ul>
<li>指针的数据类型要和指向变量的类型保持一致</li>
</ul>
<div class="code-container" data-rel="C"><figure class="iseeu highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> a =<span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span>* p=&amp;a;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//指针p的数据类型就要和变量a的数据类型一样</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>

<p><strong>为了方便理解指针变量和指针，以及地址的关系：</strong></p>
 <div class="code-container" data-rel="C"><figure class="iseeu highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"> <span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;stdlib.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;string.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;math.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;time.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;stdint.h&gt;</span> <span class="comment">// 引入stdint.h以支持固定宽度整数类型</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title function_">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">{</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> a = <span class="number">20</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span>* p = &amp;a;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 使用 intptr_t 或 uintptr_t 来存储指针值，避免精度丢失</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">uintptr_t</span> q = (<span class="type">uintptr_t</span>)&amp;a; <span class="comment">// 将指针转换为无符号整数类型</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"地址指向的值: %d\n"</span>, *p); <span class="comment">// 打印地址指向的值</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"地址值: %zu\n"</span>, q);        <span class="comment">// 打印地址值，使用%zu格式化输出</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"指针变量的大小是%zu个字节\n"</span>, <span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(p)); <span class="comment">// 指针变量的大小</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"指针变量指向的变量大小为%zu个字节\n"</span>, <span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(*p)); <span class="comment">// 指针指向的变量大小</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    system(<span class="string">"pause"</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>

<p><strong>其中输出的结果为：</strong><br>![[Pasted image 20250318171413.png]]</p>
<ul>
<li>**这说明了变量a的地址为：167516305340</li>
<li><strong>这个地址中存储的值是20</strong></li>
<li><strong>指针变量的所指向的变量是int型的变量a,所占用的字节为4</strong></li>
<li><strong>指针变量所占用的字节大小为8（64位操作系统）</strong>，说明了指针变量占用的大小和数据类型无关而与编译器有关</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="指针的作用"><a href="#指针的作用" class="headerlink" title="指针的作用"></a>指针的作用</h2><h3 id="查询数据（查询地址中存储的数据）、修改数据"><a href="#查询数据（查询地址中存储的数据）、修改数据" class="headerlink" title="查询数据（查询地址中存储的数据）、修改数据"></a>查询数据（查询地址中存储的数据）、修改数据</h3><p><font color="red">注意：在定义变量的时候的int* p中的 * 只是一个标志，表示这是一个指针，在查询数据的时候比如printf（”%d”,* p）；这里的 * 表示的是解引用运算符，是通过对后面的内存地址查找到对应储存的数据</font></p>
<div class="code-container" data-rel="C"><figure class="iseeu highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> a=<span class="number">20</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span>* p=&amp;a;<span class="comment">//这里的 * 只是表示这是一个指针，指针变量是p</span></span><br><span class="line">*p <span class="comment">//这里是解引用，是通过内存地址查找到对应的数据，相当于 *内存地址，找到对应的地址中存储的值，同时这里也说明了一个信息，我可以通过查找到对应数据的内存地址来对数据的值进行修改</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>

<h2 id="形参不改变实参"><a href="#形参不改变实参" class="headerlink" title="形参不改变实参"></a><strong>形参不改变实参</strong></h2><p>在函数里边的操作，如果是设置没有返回值的函数，那么不会改变main函数里边的值<br>实例：</p>
<div class="code-container" data-rel="C"><figure class="iseeu highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">swap</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> a, <span class="type">int</span> b)</span><span class="comment">//形参</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">{</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> temp = a;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    a = b;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    b = temp;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">}</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title function_">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">{</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> a = <span class="number">20</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> b=<span class="number">30</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    swap(a,b);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"a=%d,b=%d\n"</span>,a,b);</span><br><span class="line">    system(<span class="string">"pause"</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>

<p><strong>以上代码运行的结果：</strong><br>![[Pasted image 20250318173926.png]]<br>即我们在函数中交换了数据，但是在main函数中并不受影响，这就是值传递，传递的是形参。<br>可以初略的理解为，在main中有两个变量，将这两个变量传递给我们写的函数，在这里，我们只是将变量是数值传递给了函数，相当于在函数中用了两个新的变量去接收这两数值，但是在main函数中，并没有改变原本的变量中的数值，这是分开的。</p>
<p>如果需要将改变的结果在main函数中体现，可以用实参传递：</p>
<div class="code-container" data-rel="C"><figure class="iseeu highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">swap</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> *a,<span class="type">int</span> *b)</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">{</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> temp = *a;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    *a = *b;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    *b = temp;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">}</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title function_">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">{</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> a = <span class="number">20</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> b=<span class="number">30</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    swap(&amp;a,&amp;b);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"a=%d,b=%d\n"</span>,a,b);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    system(<span class="string">"pause"</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>

<p>对地址中储存的值进行操作，因为其中传入的地址是原本main函数中的两个变量的地址，所以可以修改。<br>运行的结果如下：<br>![[Pasted image 20250318174911.png]]</p>
<h2 id="结合内存四区-补充）"><a href="#结合内存四区-补充）" class="headerlink" title="结合内存四区(补充）"></a><strong>结合内存四区(补充）</strong></h2><p>众所周知，我们内存被划分为四个区，代码区，全局区，栈区，堆区。<br>其中，栈区的代码有程序结束后由编译器自动释放，堆区有我们手动开辟，手动释放（一般我们写构造函数和析构函数的时候就会体会到）</p>
<p>其中全局区，存放全局变量，静态变量和常量<br>栈区：存放局部变量，函数的参数值等</p>
<p>如果我们并不想将我们已经得出的结果放在栈区（函数运行结束后，我们的结果也会随之消失，那块内存被编译器释放），所以我们需要在其中我们所需要的变量前面添加关键字static（在函数内的我们所需要保留的变量前面添加，这样这个变量就会保存到程序运行结束</p>
<div class="code-container" data-rel="C"><figure class="iseeu highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title function_">math</span><span class="params">()</span></span><br><span class="line">{</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">static</span> <span class="type">int</span> a=<span class="number">20</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> &amp;a;</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>

<p>如果在函数中需要返回多个值，也可以使用指针。这样写<br>其中，我们直接修改的是地址中的值，不需要返回。所以用void。</p>
<div class="code-container" data-rel="C"><figure class="iseeu highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">getnum</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> arr[],<span class="type">int</span> len, <span class="type">int</span> &amp;max, <span class="type">int</span> &amp;min)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>

<p>同用的，我们可以利用在地址中修改数据的性质，将计算状态和函数结果进行一个分开。</p>
<div class="code-container" data-rel="C"><figure class="iseeu highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title function_">text</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> a,<span class="type">int</span> b,<span class="type">int</span>* c)</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">{</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(b==<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    {<span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;}</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    {</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">       *c=a%b;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    }</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">}</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title function_">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">{</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> a,b,c;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> d=text(a,b,&amp;c);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(d!=<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    {</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"计算成功，余数为：%d\n"</span>,c);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    }</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    {</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"计算失败\n"</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    }</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    system(<span class="string">"pause"</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>

<p>这里只是将函数text作为一个判断，如果理解不了，可以换一种思路</p>
<div class="code-container" data-rel="Cpp"><figure class="iseeu highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">bool</span> <span class="title">text</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> a,<span class="type">int</span> b, <span class="type">int</span>*c)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>{</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(b==<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(b!=<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    {</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        *c=a/b;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    }</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">}</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>{</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> a=<span class="number">10</span>,b=<span class="number">2</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> c=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">bool</span> d=<span class="built_in">text</span>(a,b,&amp;c);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="keyword">if</span>(d!=<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">   {</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"计算成功\n"</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">   }</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"%d\n"</span>,c);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">system</span>(<span class="string">"pause"</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
]]></content>
